channel.title: Some things to edit in the deob
channel.description:
[size=18pt]WARNING! DO NOT LOG ONTO RUNESCAPE USING A DEOB OR YOU WILL BE BANNED! THIS IS JUST TO HAVE FUN WITH A NEW ACCOUNT![/size]
Yes this is for the 457/458 client so if this is still not aloud, sorry, just delete it. I was going through some of the classes looking for stuff and I just searched for some quote marks and found some interesting things lol. A lot of these are sprite names, so check some of those out. Anyways, here are all my finds... please don't leech, post if you like
[code]Class2 - "Take" Class5_Sub1 - "redstone1" Class6 - " million", "titlebox" Class7 - "wishes to duel with you", "headicons_pk", "type", "close" Class8 - "remove", "dummy" Class9 - "(X" (X button?), "private chat" Class11 - "accept trade" Class13 - "cabbage" Class13_Sub2 - "mapmarker", "friends" Class14 - "backleft2" Class16 - "mapedge" Class17 - "hitmarks" Class18 - "choose option" Class20 - "backvmd3", "public chat" Class22 - "message" Class24 - "backright2" Class25 - "attack", "enter amount" Class31 - "runes", "accept challenge" Class36 - "Nov", "Apr", "Jul", "Feb", "Mar", "Sep", "May", "Jan", "Jun", "Oct", "Dec", "Aug" Class37 - "sl_back", "Moderator option: Mute player for 48 hours: <OFF>", "Username: ", "compass" Class41 - "mapscene", "backhmid2" Class43 - " more options" Class54 - "cross", "drop" Class55 - "backtop1", "World" Class56 - "::clientdrop" Class58 - "This computers address has been blocked" Class59 - "backvmid2" Class61 - "headicons_prayer" Class62 - "Offline" Class63 - "Continue" Class72 - "Walk here", "click here to switch", "backhmid1" Class73 - "Please try again)3" Class74 - "scrollbar" Class75 - " has logged in)3", "cancel" Class76 - "off" Class77 - "Benutzername: " (username?) Class78 - "redstone2", "redstone3", "Helvetica" (a font) Class79 - "c:/windows/" (and some other things dealing with rs cache)[/code]
